      "description": "The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} spends 5 feet of movement to jump to a space within 15 feet that contains one or more Large or smaller creatures.\n\nDexterity Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=IPCXEQoTuaAG5l52]], each [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=IPCXEQoTuaAG5l52]] in the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s destination space.\n\nFailure: [[/damage average]] damage, and the target has the &amp;Reference[Prone apply=false] condition.\n\nSuccess: Half damage, and the target is pushed 5 feet straight away from the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}.",
